    <h1><%[Paste-it Help Center]%></h1>
    <p><%[Paste-it is a debugging colaborative tool, which helps you to debug the application with the help of other people.]%></p>
    <h2><%[Colaborative what? How does it works?]%></h2>
    <p><%[You post your wrong code and send it to somebody on IRC, IM, e-mail, or anything. The person changes your code and send you back the new URL. Now your have the corrected (or suggested) code and a diff page (that uses the same syntax of a diff file).]%></p>
    <h2><%[What can Paste-it do to me?]%></h2>
    <p>
        <%[Paste-it currently has:]%>
        <ul>
            <li><%[support for <b>16 languages code highlight</b> (and couting..!)]%></li>
            <li><%[you can add <b>named blocks of codes</b> just by add a line that begins with "===Block Name". It's cool and simple!]%></li>
            <li><%[<b>diff page</b> to you understand what have changed in your code or text file]%></li>
            <li><%[paste-it <b>remembers you</b>! Paste-it beleaves that you are human (not a spammer bot) after the last time you have been here...]%></li>
            <li><%[private post]%></li>
        </ul>
    </p>
    <h2><%[What is coming soon?]%></h2>
    <ul>
        <li><%[file upload]%></li>
        <li><%[more languages support]%></li>
        <li><%[a command line tool (such as <a href="http://n01se.net/agriffis/nopaste/">nopaste</a>)]%></li>
    </ul>
